SENATE BILL 420 5
1 1. The University of Maryland Center for Environmental
2 Studies;
3 2. The University of Maryland Global Campus; or
4 3. The University of Baltimore OF ANY AGE; OR
5 (3) SHARES PARENTAL RESPONSIBILITIES WITH SOMEONE IN THE
6 SAME HOUSEHOLD OR A DIFFERENT HOUSEHOLD] OF ANY AGE; OR
7 (3) SHARES PARENTAL RESPONSIBILITIES WITH SOMEONE IN
